data.description: Super cute, well maintained with great curb appeal located in a great area of River Ridge!  "X" Flood zone. Light and bright! 3BD/1BA with a spacious back yard and large storage shed. Over-sized laundry room (18' x 10') with great storage! Lots of kitchen cabinets, pretty granite counters, gas range/oven and breakfast area with banquette seating.  No carpet. Tankless water heater.  Brick and vinyl siding exterior.  Driveway parking for two vehicles. Convenient area close shopping, restaurants, banking and more!
